graph LR
    TrustyAI[TrustyAI Service Operator]

    %% External Platform Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|orchestration| Kubernetes[Kubernetes v1.19+]
    TrustyAI -.->|optional routes/oauth| OpenShift[OpenShift v4.6+]
    TrustyAI -->|metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1]
    TrustyAI -.->|optional mesh| Istio[Istio latest]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|watch/patch CRs| KServe[KServe v0.12.1]
    TrustyAI -->|label discovery| ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving]
    TrustyAI -->|expose metrics| Prometheus[Prometheus UWM]
    TrustyAI -.->|discoverable by| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% Optional Integration Points
    TrustyAI -.->|workload mgmt| Kueue[Kueue v0.6.2]
    TrustyAI -.->|storage backend| Database[(Database<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL)]

    %% Reverse dependencies (components that use TrustyAI)
    KServe -->|sends inference data| TrustyAI
    Dashboard -->|service discovery| TrustyAI
    Prometheus -->|scrape metrics| TrustyAI

    %% External Services
    TrustyAI -.->|optional storage| S3[S3 Storage]

    %% Kubernetes API
    TrustyAI -->|CRD reconciliation| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Styling
    style TrustyAI fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (required)
    style Kubernetes fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style PrometheusOp fill:#e6522c,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#326ce5,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% External dependencies (optional)
    style OpenShift fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Istio fill:#466bb0,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Kueue fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Database fill:#4479a1,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style S3 fill:#ff9900,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH components
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#000
